"},"source":["**How to Interpret:** <br>\n","Lots of stuff going on here! But boy is it a great way to get a good sense for the time series data.\n","1. Each row is a different feature, with the time series on the left, and the histogram on the right.\n","2. Red color at the base of each row plot marks where data is *missing*, NA. The green percentage represents the proportion of data present for that given year.\n","3. Lastly, there is the descriptive statistics: missing, min, max, mean, median, 95th percentile"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"_cell_guid":"427cca8c-fcfe-4d99-af27-9ba9378ad89c","_uuid":"da1f4acb1021388d1aac85ac4afc705055ec7944"},"source":["## Time Series\n","**Calendar Plot:** <br>\n","This one I am particularly fond of since it is exremely intuitive. **Red Alert!** October 20 to 21 had **Bad SO2!**"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":4,"metadata":{"_cell_guid":"e3535183-023e-43ae-9ba7-be608b8fee9a","_uuid":"6743506e7369ba2831e38da9f641ad67fe5ee6c3","execution":{"iopub.execute_input":"2026-05-15T12:33:03.198225Z","iopub.status.busy":"2026-05-15T12:33:03.197416Z","iopub.status.idle":"2026-05-15T12:33:05.260277Z","shell.execute_reply":"2026-05-15T12:33:05.259718Z"}},"outputs":[{"data":{"image/png":"iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAlgAAAHgCAIAAAD2dYQOAAAABmJLR0QA/wD/AP+gvaeTAAAg\nAElEQVR4nOzdZ1wTSQMG8GdTCYQqIAoCYkXFghQBC/Z6Vuzl9Kynop531tfe251nPXtvZy+I\nYi8URRD17AoqgiC9BEhIyL4fgogYSNhFAZn/Lx+STfbJ7CSbyezO7lI0TYMgCIIgKipOaReA\nIAiCIEoTaQgJgiCICo00hARBEESFRhpCgiAIokIjDSFBEARRoZGGkCAIgqjQSENIEARBVGik\nISQIgiAqNNIQEgRBEBUaaQiJckwSGfS/MUPaNXeqZqYvMrJwcPLoOWDEpqM35IWfLik79cW2\nVf/r3srRpqq5Dl9oalGtUbOOvy/ecO9D5ncsOEEQZQlNEOWS8sCMfvrc3H9yHK5IxPv8r66K\n25AXmfKv57m0dqKVDk/tisDhGQ/+3365km2x7k5poArMymEblSc94vbcsQNbuTayMNIxtKju\n3rbbH3+fzFSXnyP7sG7WaMea1fQEPEPTqm7dft59413R4bJUfx5FNVlwX+2zkRfbF/bTYd74\nHPtFI4iygDSERLn03/ouqp/jTqPmBz1/l5WjpHNkMW9f7F46obqIB8DcaU6BWfZOaK6axaJp\nr3V7z754G52eKYmJDPc7smWop53qqTq9F2ezawtLvCH8GLimioCryuSLK4m4lOq+cb3OtxOy\n8r9SnvG8s61+brv